name: The Wind Will Take Us With It

metadata.name: Inner Light
metadata.description:
Everyone has an inner light,
Which can guide them through life.
Sometimes it may seem dim, or it may even seem completely off.
But, it will always come back again, for it is the light that guides us and keeps us warm.
So, if you ever feel like you have lost yours, or it has been switched off,
Just remember that it will always come back again,
Because it is an essential part of who you are.
